			surname: "Haazebroek",
			affiliation: "University of Leiden",
			description: "I am a computer scientist and cognitive psychologist working in the areas of cognitivemodeling, computational neuroscience and cognitive systems. The goal of myresearch is to gain understanding of the computational mechanisms underlying humancognition, perception and action planning and to build intelligent systems that makeuse of these insights."
